00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.115
Early in the course when we're looking at HTML and the problems which it solves.

00:00:05.115 --> 00:00:08.280
We mentioned, the hypertext is the text displayed on

00:00:08.280 --> 00:00:12.360
a computer which links to other texts or documents.

00:00:12.360 --> 00:00:15.015
These links are called hyperlinks.

00:00:15.015 --> 00:00:18.105
We already have our menu items,

00:00:18.105 --> 00:00:19.980
just like the example here.

00:00:19.980 --> 00:00:24.645
But we need a way to change them to the links to other pages.

00:00:24.645 --> 00:00:29.565
To do this, we have a element which stands for anchor.

00:00:29.565 --> 00:00:32.205
We can use it to link to other pages,

00:00:32.205 --> 00:00:34.620
different locations on the same page,

00:00:34.620 --> 00:00:37.335
or even other websites too.

00:00:37.335 --> 00:00:42.120
Let's get to work by adding links to our menu items.

00:00:42.120 --> 00:00:45.035
Let's go over to the index page,

00:00:45.035 --> 00:00:49.145
and let's go over to our header, up at the top.

00:00:49.145 --> 00:00:51.600
These three links here,

00:00:51.650 --> 00:00:57.125
first links adds the a element around what we want to link.

00:00:57.125 --> 00:01:00.445
In our case, we want to link the text here.

00:01:00.445 --> 00:01:04.530
I'm just going to cut this out and then open

00:01:04.530 --> 00:01:08.550
up the a element which is opening and closing.

00:01:08.550 --> 00:01:13.100
In the middle here we can paste in our home link once more.

00:01:13.100 --> 00:01:16.345
This means our text is going to be clickable.

00:01:16.345 --> 00:01:19.520
Then we add the location we want to link to,

00:01:19.520 --> 00:01:21.815
by adding the href attribute,

00:01:21.815 --> 00:01:24.740
which stands for hyperlink reference.

00:01:24.740 --> 00:01:28.050
Inside the opening a tag, href,

00:01:28.050 --> 00:01:34.965
just H-R-E-F. Then inside this href,

00:01:34.965 --> 00:01:36.735
we can add a link.

00:01:36.735 --> 00:01:39.585
Let's link to a random website,

00:01:39.585 --> 00:01:42.740
let's say the Mozilla website which we visited earlier,

00:01:42.740 --> 00:01:46.080
so http://developer.mozilla.org,

00:01:53.710 --> 00:01:55.960
and save that,

00:01:55.960 --> 00:01:59.445
over to the browser, refresh.

00:01:59.445 --> 00:02:01.835
Then back up to the top of the page.

00:02:01.835 --> 00:02:05.410
We can see instantly that there's a change with the home link.

00:02:05.410 --> 00:02:08.955
If we hover over it, we now see a different cursor.

00:02:08.955 --> 00:02:11.780
It's also a different color with the underline,

00:02:11.780 --> 00:02:13.655
which shows it's a link.

00:02:13.655 --> 00:02:16.450
Let's click on this and see what happens.

00:02:16.450 --> 00:02:21.630
Then we link in to this developer.mozilla.org website,

00:02:21.630 --> 00:02:23.880
that's all working fine.

00:02:23.880 --> 00:02:27.745
We hit the back button were taken back to our index page.

00:02:27.745 --> 00:02:33.220
This is an external link because we are linking away from our own website.

00:02:33.220 --> 00:02:38.975
We can also create an internal link to link to another page in our project too.

00:02:38.975 --> 00:02:42.795
Let's create some more web pages to link to.

00:02:42.795 --> 00:02:45.645
Back over to the project.

00:02:45.645 --> 00:02:48.735
Let's go over to our text tile,

00:02:48.735 --> 00:02:51.645
make sure you're not clicking on the images folder.

00:02:51.645 --> 00:02:55.995
We'll click off this and then click on new file.

00:02:55.995 --> 00:03:03.160
Make sure this new file is outside the images folder and alongside this index.html.

00:03:03.160 --> 00:03:08.380
Then let's save this contact with the dot HTML extension,

00:03:08.380 --> 00:03:10.720
just like the index page.

00:03:10.720 --> 00:03:18.300
Then let's just add some simple text of contact us page, save that.

00:03:18.300 --> 00:03:23.490
Then let's do one more too, new file.

00:03:23.490 --> 00:03:26.350
Then let's call this the product-detail.

00:03:28.850 --> 00:03:32.400
Again with a dot HTML extension.

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:36.625
Just add some text or product detail page.

