we want this to link back to this index page.

00:04:13.100 --> 00:04:18.675
You give that a save and then we click on this.

00:04:18.675 --> 00:04:22.955
We can see nothing changes because it's still link on to this index page,

00:04:22.955 --> 00:04:29.235
and of course we still taken this index page. Now for the shop.

00:04:29.235 --> 00:04:33.750
If we cut out the shop texts looking as the link with the a tag,

00:04:33.750 --> 00:04:35.585
and paste this in the middle.

00:04:35.585 --> 00:04:38.420
We don't have a shop page just yet,

00:04:38.420 --> 00:04:41.780
