00:04:48.680 --> 00:04:50.810
Then the contact us page,

00:04:50.810 --> 00:04:53.480
which is one of the pages which we just created.

00:04:53.480 --> 00:04:56.135
Let's open up the a tags.

00:04:56.135 --> 00:05:02.250
Paste contact us inside the middle, the href attribute.

00:05:02.260 --> 00:05:06.630
This time it's contact.html.

