00:06:31.495 --> 00:06:36.300
Let's look for the images which we added before.

00:06:36.300 --> 00:06:43.200
This, let's copy it and all we're going to do is keep copying and pasting this in.

00:06:43.510 --> 00:06:48.985
Just give us a more content on the page and give that a save.

00:06:48.985 --> 00:06:51.650
Then if we refresh the browser,

00:06:51.650 --> 00:06:54.865
we now have some content we can scroll down to.

00:06:54.865 --> 00:06:58.130
This will allow us to click on a link and

00:06:58.130 --> 00:07:01.520
