00:07:01.520 --> 00:07:04.645
This is possible by adding a ID,

00:07:04.645 --> 00:07:07.365
so lets add an ID to one of these products.

00:07:07.365 --> 00:07:12.025
At the very start an ID is just an attribute like we've seen before.

